title: Week 4: Operation Sports Fantasy Football Championship on FanDuel
text: 03:46 PM - September 30, 2015 by Steve_OS Three weeks down, 14 weeks to go in the season of all seasons -- the NFL season. Week 3 brought us a lot of craziness. From DeVonte Freeman and his three touchdowns to LeGarrette Blount and his three touchdowns to Aaron Rodgers and his FIVE touchdowns -- there were some crazy high point totals last week. Before we dig into the winning lineup from Week 3 of The Operation Sports FanDuel Championship , heres what you need to know about Week 4: The contest costs $5 to play and pays $100 to first place. Click here to enter ! We'll see you there! The winning lineup from Week 3, submitted by nolimitfantasyfootball , saw A LOT of points scored -- Freeman nearly hit forty points while Aaron Rodgers, Larry Fitzgerald and Latavius Murray nearly hit thirty points for a grand total of 213. A very hearty congratulations to nolimitfantasyfootball for his dominating performance, beating the second place finisher, green757, by over 16 points!
